$pip install Django
- will insatall django libraries

 Go to the required location and
 $ django-admin startproject <mysite>
 - wil create a project named <mysite> with some default files
 
 Go to the main directory using cd ... and 
 $ python manage.py runserver
 --this will start the server in http://127.0.0.1:8000/
 
 if required in different port then
 $ python manage.py runserver 89
 --this will start the server in http://127.0.0.1:89/
